
Ranger Help for: move
=====================

SYNTAX:      move silently/move normally
USAGE:       forest,plains,swamp,desert,jungle,hills,road,inside,
             beach,underground,mountain,arctic,barren,outside
SLOT COST:   6
BASE SP:     20 sp/5 sp per move
SKILL TYPE:  defensive

SUMMARY:    
In certain terrains, once a Ranger has learned this skill, he or she
can move through the area silently. Other players can see you, but
they can't hear you enter or leave via normal exits.

